Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向您詢問幾個問題並確認一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想提問就先摘下護目鏡  報上名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝王鬥技正統  海蒂·E·S·英格瓦爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我自稱為「霸王」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞中的路上劫匪麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不否認
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你想問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於您相熟的那兩位「王」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖王奧利維爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和冥府的炎王伊克斯威莉婭的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為您清楚她們二位的所在…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖王也好  冥王殿下也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得自己認識那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:00:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是努力生活著的  平凡的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我會向別人詢問
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  關於另一個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要確認的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的拳頭和我的拳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰的更強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:03:00.63,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(346,620)\be2}「愛因哈特·斯崔特斯」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.44,0:03:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請換上防護服和武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看這不還是個小屁孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道自己有多強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  真是可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…看來不全是吹牛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(618,646)\fs36}Jet Edge
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾捷風棱！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}Start Up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深表謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你想知道自己有多強？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我想變得比現在更強大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去認真練習或者向著職業格鬥家方向努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是喜歡打架的話就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我可以介紹一些好的道館和道場給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想確認的強度——生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公開的舞台上是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就擺架勢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣的距離？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是射擊型的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有必須要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要做的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒所有的列強諸王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱霸貝魯卡世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我一直想要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說夢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的那些王都已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倖存下來的和那些後裔們全都過著平凡的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於弱小的王來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有活下去的意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝魯卡的戰亂也好  聖王戰爭也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連貝魯卡這個國家本身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都早就已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄防禦來施放束縛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還都沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷  空  拳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱小是一種罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為弱小的拳頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒辦法保護任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的那一擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的打擊力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這副身體的確很強大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可因為我內心的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武裝形態解除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去之後稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一覺醒來再…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒在這裏的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(545,646)\fs36}Jet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾捷  沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}I'm ok
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我聯繫昴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:07:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,646)\fs36}All right
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:07:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是昴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  稍微幫我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾威  你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架的時候挨了一記狠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是之前提過的那個襲擊犯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也給了她不小的打擊  定位儀也裝上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在去應該可以立刻捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾威  你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在迪亞正在辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不能亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不還是個孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是個有故事的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  能過段時間再帶她去所裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帶到我家去會比較好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來  謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利維爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  還沒有分出勝負…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你無論如何也要作為明君跟國民一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能讓這片大地不會再因戰爭而乾枯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造隨時都能看到藍天和美麗的花朵的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的國家…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能去搖籃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利維爾  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利維爾  奧利維爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最悲傷的記憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  你終於醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽你嘟囔個不停  沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…這裏是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  諾威
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有自稱霸王英格瓦爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本名愛因哈特·斯崔特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖·希爾德魔法學院中等科一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我翻了一下儲物櫃裏的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  東西都在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把制服和學生證帶在身邊  還真是個糊塗的打架王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是放學路上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且沒想到在那種地方倒下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早飯久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,培根煎蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜湯不夠還可以加喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  愛因哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是昴·中島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想你也有很多緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先吃早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊吃邊告訴我  你看好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那姑且先說明一下我們的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是這傢伙  我家老姐昴的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個消防員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是昴的摯友  總局執行官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫迪亞娜·蘭絲達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你保護起來的就是這兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說謝謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以針對格鬥家的連續襲擊犯就是你…這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告訴我們理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說在她心中  遠古時代的貝魯卡戰爭還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  想知道自己有多強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  想把聖王和冥王打翻在地？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後那個有點不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為霸王  比古代貝魯卡的任何一個王都要強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能夠證明這一點就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我無法原諒弱小的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說  和聖王家和冥王家並沒有仇是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為昴和那兩個人關係很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要涼了  不介意的話就快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  等會兒一起去趟警防署總局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也挺擔心你的身體的  讓他們檢查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然沒人提交受害報告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你保證不再在街上找人打架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該馬上就可以放你回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是當事人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦電波沒有異常  身體方面也很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  她身為貝魯卡王族後裔的事也是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫局有記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出過什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她是記憶繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶繼承？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癥狀是繼承了自己以外的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如父母或者祖先的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是非常罕見的病癥  所以記錄了她的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…就是說…這到底是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種病也是因人而異  不能一概而論
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就她的情況而言  她可以把她的祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的王  克勞斯·英格瓦爾特的記憶和知識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是自己的記憶一樣回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同他所經歷的事乃至感情  各種各樣的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  一般來說繼承來的記憶會慢慢淡去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在今後的生活中增添快樂的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起過去的情況應該也會減少的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  迪亞  難得你不值班
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也一樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我說你啊  總能碰到貝魯卡的王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還「是啊」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那孩子…愛因哈特看上去還有很多心結
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放著不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那個可愛的妹妹似乎挺願意幫忙的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還有那麼多必須要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渾身破綻啊  霸王小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該馬上就會放你走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後打算幹什麼去？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天學校不上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家老姐還有迪亞娜在局裏也算身手不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們還認識許多瞭解古代貝魯卡系的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道你說的那個「戰爭」是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是有能幫上你的地方  我們會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「所以不要對聖王她們出手」是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  這麼說也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出手的話我也會很頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和強者戰鬥  變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後證明霸王流的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種心情  我還是能明白一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也有一段胡鬧的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情總是很不爽  不管碰到誰都想先打一架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我並不喜歡打架和暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那時候的我除此之外什麼都不會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你  喜歡格鬥技吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也還是修行之身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有在學習教練的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑒別才能和心境的眼光應該還是不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對嗎  你不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡還是討厭  我從來沒有考慮過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝王鬥技是我存在的全部理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  能不能告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王流的事  你的國家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你銘記在心的戰爭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  狀態不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  開始下一個項目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  克莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾威發來的郵件？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲特媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲特媽媽  可以一起洗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦  進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈葉也？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為菲特媽媽  今天就要出航了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能在一起的時間就在一起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲特  好久沒幫你洗頭髮了  我來給你洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕  我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲今天也很努力地陪我一起訓練哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  大家對克莉絲的正式名字有沒有說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是「果然」啦「好名字」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆背著我說什麼悄悄話呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  奈葉  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天午飯想吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下要和莉奧和珂羅娜在圖書館集合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有點想查的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  找到要找的書了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  這些這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「霸王英格瓦爾特傳」和「雄王列記」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有當時的歷史書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  珂羅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是之前露推薦給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是怎麼了？  突然找些修托拉的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  諾威說想一起學這方面的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王英格瓦爾特和聖王奧利維爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是什麼樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位都是充滿謎團的王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種書給出的解釋也不盡相同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也有寫「根據現代歷史的研究  兩者的關係還不明確」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖王奧利維爾明明是大名人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  啊  還有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾威她新認識了個練格鬥技的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我們要不要和她一起練習
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:40.91,NETITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(152,720)\1cA7B90F}「認真的心情」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道愛因哈特同學是個什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.09,0:23:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望是個溫柔的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…Lyrical Magical  我會加油的

